name: HTMLShadowElement
description: Obsolete This feature is obsolete. Although it may still work in some browsers, its use is discouraged since it could be removed at any time. Try to avoid using it. The HTMLShadowElement interface represents a <shadow> HTML Element, which is used in Shadow DOM.
